 <div xml:id="translation" type="section">
 <head>Translation:</head>
 <p>
 <lb n="1"/>Decided by the Dēmos. Those in <placeName key="Salamis"
 >Salamis</placeName> who are cleruchs <lb n="2"/>shall be allowed to reside
 on <placeName key="Salamis">Salamis</placeName> … at Athens <lb n="3"
 />to pay taxes and provide military service. But what is theirs on <placeName
 key="Salamis">Salamis</placeName>
 <lb n="4"/>shall not be leased, unless a kinsman(?) is the lessor. If <lb n="5"
 />someone should lease it, the lessee shall pay a penalty, and the lessee, <lb
 n="6"/>each of them … <lb n="7"/>to the public treasury. And the
 <term sortKey="archon">archon</term> shall handle by the transaction,
 <lb n="8"/>if not, he shall be held accountable at his <foreign xml:lang="xgrc">
 <w xml:lang="xgrc" n="eu)/quna">euthyna</w>
 </foreign>. <lb n="9"/>They shall furnish the weapons themselves; <lb n="10"
 />the cost is thirty drachmas. Having been armed <lb n="11"/>the <term sortKey="archon">archon</term> shall inspect their weapons. <lb n="12"
 />The <term sortKey="Council">boulē</term>, in the year of
 …</p>
